race.comment: MIDNIGHT SPIRIT (1) has been right there in all three runs this preparation and looks to be building up to another victory. Will be ready to peak now fourth run in and gets the reliable Gollan/Maloney combination. Rates the testing material. HA'PENNY HATCH (3) loves it here around the Eagle Farm circuit with two wins and two seconds from just five spins. Rarely puts in a poor one and has to be included in calculations. CRASH THE PARTY (10) strip fitter third-up from the break and did get up to Listed level when last in work. Top-three conveyance. SMEXY (5) has hit the top-four in all four career outings and looks a must for the multiples. BOOMSHANKA (8) rounds out the selections.
